Title : Vampire Prosecutor (K-Drama) (2011)
Alternative Title(s) : Vampire Geumsa / Vampire Prosecutor
Hardsubbed or Softsubbed: Softsubbed
English Subtitles: Yes
Number of Episodes: 12
Resolution: 800 x 450
Date Aired (YYYY-MM-DD): 2011-Oct-02
More Info: http://wiki.d-addicts.com/Vampire_Prosecutor



Summary: Prosecutor Min Tae Yeon (Yun Jung Hoon) is bitten by somebody and becomes a Vampire. Tae Yeon rejects the life of a vampire and he survives by drinking the blood of dead people and still lives as a righteous prosecutor . Tae Yeon also uses his new founded abilities as a Vampire to prosecute powerful persons normally thought above the law. A mysterious case then occurs and the evidence points to a Vampire as the perpetrator. Tae Yeon now knows that he is not the only Vampire. He also ponders why he became a Vampire and what truths may lie behind their motives.
